#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Security audits and advisories\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Auditories i advertències de seguretat\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc levels=3]]\n"
msgstr "[[!toc levels=3]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Since Tails is based on Debian, it takes advantage of all the work done by "
"the Debian security team. As quoted from <https://www.debian.org/security/>:"
msgstr ""
"Com que Tails es basa en Debian, aprofita tot el treball realitzat per "
"l'equip de seguretat de Debian. Com es cita a <https://www.debian.org/"
"security/>:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> Debian takes security very seriously. We handle all security\n"
"problems brought to our attention and ensure that they are corrected within a\n"
"reasonable timeframe. Many advisories are coordinated with other free software\n"
"vendors and are published the same day a vulnerability is made public and we\n"
"also have a Security Audit team that reviews the archive looking for new or\n"
"unfixed security bugs.\n"
msgstr ""
"> Debian es pren la seguretat molt seriosament. Gestionem tots els problemes\n"
"de seguretat que se'ns posen en coneixement i ens assegurem que es corregeixen\n"
"en un termini raonable. Molts avisos es coordinen amb altres venedors de programari\n"
"lliure i es publiquen el mateix dia que es fa pública una vulnerabilitat i també tenim\n"
"un equip d'Auditoria de seguretat que revisa l'arxiu buscant errors de seguretat\n"
"nous o no solucionats.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> Experience has shown that \"security through obscurity\" does\n"
"not work. Public disclosure allows for more rapid and better solutions to\n"
"security problems. In that vein, this page addresses Debian's status with\n"
"respect to various known security vulnerabilities, which could potentially affect\n"
"Debian.\n"
msgstr ""
"> L'experiència ha demostrat que «la seguretat a través de l'obscuritat» no\n"
"funciona. La divulgació pública permet solucions més ràpides i millors als\n"
"problemes de seguretat. En aquest sentit, aquesta pàgina aborda l'estat de\n"
"Debian pel que fa a diverses vulnerabilitats de seguretat conegudes, que\n"
"podrien afectar Debian.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"See also our [[security issue response policy|contribute/security_policy]]."
msgstr ""
"Consulteu la nostra [[política de resposta als problemes de seguretat|"
"contribute/security_policy]]."

